t: "Ndaarndee wondu…ďe …ďen si …ďe yottike desal, si on so'ii e ma…ď…ďe peewal, jonnitee…ďe jawle ma…ďe …óen, wata on √Īaamir …óe faŇčtinngol e hawjugol …óoo yo …ďe mawnude. On taw…óo ko o galo, yo o naŇčto, on taw…óo ko o baaso, yo o √Īaamir no mo∆ī∆īiri. Si on jonnitii…ďe jawle ma…ď…ďe …óen, seedinee e dow ma…ď…ďe. Alla Yonii Hasboowo"